      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Those feelings of invisibility and worthlessness are incredibly heavy to carry alone, and it validates that you deserve support from someone who hears your pain without trying to fix it immediately. Your life holds value, even when it feels buried under routines and screens, but recognizing that disconnect is often the first step toward healing. Please reach out to a crisis line or therapist today to find a safe space where you can rest without the pressure of convincing anyone you matter. You are not replaceable, even if the world right now doesn't seem to reflect that truth.",
